properties.Name: InsurancePolicyEndorsement
properties.Description: The Endorsement(s) that are attached to the general Insurance Policy.

Columns.Name: InsurancePolicyId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of an Insurance Policy.

Columns.Name: InsuranceEndorsementId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of an Insurance Endorsement.

Columns.Name: PeriodStartDate
Columns.Description: The period start date that the endorsement is written into the policy.

Columns.Name: PeriodEndDate
Columns.Description: The period end date that the endorsement is written into the policy.

Columns.Name: RiderAttachedDate
Columns.Description: The date that the Rider was attached.

Columns.Name: RiderOfferDate
Columns.Description: The date that the Rider was offered.

Columns.Name: RiderOfferElapseDate
Columns.Description: The date that the Rider will elapse and no longer be offered.

Columns.Name: InsurancePolicyEndorsementNote
Columns.Description: A note, comment or additional information regarding the insurance policy endorsement.
